Get a list of propositions discussed in between a time interval

proposicoes.Rd

Get a list of propositions discussed in between a time interval

proposicoes(..., from, to)

Arguments

...

query parameters for the House of Representatives API (See: https://dadosabertos.camara.leg.br/swagger/api.html)
from

start date (YYYY-MM-DD) for the time interval in which a proposition was discussed
to

end date (YYYY-MM) for the time interval in which a proposition was discussed

Value

A tibble of propositions discussed in between a time interval

See also

Other proposicoes: proposicoes_autores(), proposicoes_historico(), proposicoes_info(), proposicoes_referencias(), proposicoes_relacionadas(), proposicoes_temas(), proposicoes_votacoes()

Examples

proposicoes(from = "2020-01-01", to = "2020-12-01", itens = 100)
